uote><br />\n一係教大有人侵犯他人私隱 洩露cctv片段<br />\n一係百份報偷cctv片 偷竊 再侵犯他人私隱<br />\n睇下揀邊樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教大做乜唔去報警話有人偷片呀</blockquote><br />\n嗰度唔係公眾地方黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開放式校園姐，業權仲係教院到"},{"pid":"bdf9efde3f0e68abcec9e15183b4c80b6076790c","tid":391982,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:00:03.000Z","msg":"真係離撚譜 思想箝制"},{"pid":"fa40fd46179ff04858aa57c76221f5fed6eabecd","tid":391982,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:01:11.000Z","msg":"咁作為父母又想子女比人洗腦式唱紅？"},{"pid":"6ca421070e762aee6ff32198c42d78bb6f59f643","tid":391982,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:01:15.000Z","msg":"我唔想呢班狗官管治香港<br />\n可唔可以炒撚晒佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c62cb9f1cdeca6b8a1be649d0187516368d037","tid":391982,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"馬時亨連mtr都未管得掂"},{"pid":"a7635dda94702fdc85fdd450bb088f85b1282674","tid":391982,"uid":55732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:02:21.000Z","msg":"我係家長嘅話，我只係唔想菜肉蓮呢啲連自己個仔都唔關懷嘅臭閪做教育局咋<br />\n<br />\n講真菜肉蓮唔得掂攞飯同佢班黨羽加加埋埋累死幾十個師生，包括擎天嗰個，咁要追究都應該追究佢地謀殺啦"},{"pid":"5370e296a287794e30fed40bf57ecc2411d9d1dc","tid":391982,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/160408_6406b2321ac289e9554083dfc780d88b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F160408_6406b2321ac289e9554083dfc780d88b.jpg&h=8a967843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係向局長學習姐"},{"pid":"1e32beb6b7677c9c00f4f7b82a300c03ac42584b","tid":391982,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"合法表達意見就嚴打<br />\n非法流出閉路電視片段就視若無睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}